Huf'al: The _huf'al_ (הֻפְעַל) is one of the [[Hebrew binyanim]]. ([[{{Binyan}} is a special concept in Hebrew and Aramaic grammar]].)
- Verbs in the _huf'al_ have the properties of being [[passive]] and [[causative]].
- The _huf'al_ corresponds to the [[_itaf'al_]] in Aramaic.
- The _huf'al_ [[has various verb {{forms}}]].

